channel.title: DementionX - Looking for startup staff and some beta testers
channel.description:
[CENTER][URL=http://s1197.photobucket.com/user/RobertIsLegit/media/Welcome2demxx.png.html][IMG]http://i1197.photobucket.com/albums/aa440/RobertIsLegit/Welcome2demxx.png[/img][/URL] [url=http://www.dementionx.com]DementionX[/url][/CENTER]
Hi everyone my name is Rob im the owner of an upcoming [718] RSPS named DementionX, i am planning the release for April 1, in the next three weeks i would like to put together a small team of staff members as well as some beta testers. If you are looking and willing to contribute to a project, send me a pm on skype or reply to this thread, teamspeak would be an asset for any team member and you must be mature, thank you for your time.
Skype: demention.x
